social_posts.post_text: OFFICIAL ANNOUNCEMENT!! I have been in the studio with my brother @taystybeats in LA for the last week cooking beats and hooks for my SECOND ALBUM!! We’re already making magic and i think this project is going to be very very special. Stay tuned. #inthekitchenanditstasty.
Quick nashville recap.
About as accurate as it gets 🍺🍾.

While I work on writing this next album produced by @taystybeats, I realized I never posted my music videos in full on my Instagram. So if you haven’t watched again for the first time, feel free to enjoy here. “NEW YORK TENNECITY”. Produced by @brassxbeard. Music video by @legitlooks. Special guests @timvalleyy @caskey and @evil.eric. Comments and hate are not only invited, but encouraged.

PART 1/2:  While we’re at it, this is my verse in the second video ‘Broken Register’ feat. @bubstyles off of my album ‘Anger is a gift’ produced by @brassxbeard, and shot and directed by @legitlooks. Bubs has been and always will be my favorite rapper, and the hardest working guy in the room. If you like what you’re hearing, get excited for the project @taystybeats will be putting out in the near future. The pot is starting to simmer…

PART 2/2:  The king of gristle, aka Boars Head Bubs, aka @bubstyles verse in the second video ‘Broken Register’ Anger is a gift’ produced by @brassxbeard, and shot and directed by @legitlooks. I said it before and I’ll say it again, I’ve looked up to Bubs as an artist and a friend for a very long time. He helped give me the confidence to write my first record, learn how to find my cadences, and has always kept it real and been in my corner. This verse goes so hard it’s insulting, and I know every bar word for word.  Be sure you will be hearing more or him on my next with project @taystybeats. Shit is about to be a whole ass pastrami sandwich from Katz’s deli. 🐗🗽🛣️.

FUCK THE WORLD, HERE IS YOUR OFFICIAL LEAK OF MY NEW MUSIC. Since I’ve stole everything from @yelawolf in the past decade, I figured I’d steal @kleversworld as well to give y’all this snippet produced by @zakkgarner and @nokiobeats . I’ve been having so much fun with my homies here in nashville I figured I spread the love and show y’all what I got going on!! I’ll be out in LA with @taystybeats cutting vocals on the rest of his tracks, as well as a few more big surprises. We out here baby let’s get fired up!!!!!!!!! SLUMERICAN GANG ALL FUCKING DAY BABY.
As of lately. Love yall ❤️.
@regenaskate sent @yelawolf and myself some amazing bowls and pens made from skateboards all the way from New Zealand!!!! Appreciate you brother!!!?

@antoniapearlphotography_nz took this photo of me in New Zealand and submitted it in a gallery amongst many other beautiful photographs. Feel free to check out more of her work at https://www.photographyfestival.org.nz/photo-blog/index.cfm?start_pos=109&dir=/content/photo-blog/2023/05-May-2023_Aotearoa_Music_Photo_Award. I’m working hard on this next album, I’m already very proud of it, I can’t wait to bring it to life, and I can’t wait to get back on the road.
The muppet show lol.

Being out on the road with my friends is what I live for. I got a call from @edward.crowe a few weeks ago asking if I could come and sell merch for @yelawolf on the tour we’re currently on. Scared to jump and in the middle of writing my album, I thought it might be too big of a job for me, be it these shows are in the upwards of 15,000 people, touring with the @dirtyheads. And merch is hard. Very hard. You’re the first one in and last one out every night, carrying hundred of pounds of boxes, selling at a hundred miles an hour. But I said fuck it and bucked up. There is nothing better then spending time with my friends and supporting the @slumerican family. And it’s been a fucking blast. For @edward.crowe and @yelawolf, thank you for the trust and the opportunity, I promise to give you my all every day. And @kleversworld, you make every day brighter every time I see your face. I’ll be back on stage soon, but right now I need to take care of business.

Absolutely epic day playing golf and hanging out ⛳️🏌️‍♂️🍺 !!!! Thanks so much for having us, can’t wait to do it again!! @pga_johndaly @shydaly @johndalyll @yelawolf @visualsbytyre @txsamlee @greatdanemane @donniereismusic #oldhickory

Full recap of our round out on Old Hickory with the gang!! Had such a blast playing our scramble with the legends, and new @skallywagsgolf members @pga_johndaly @johndalyll and @shydaly, as well as your old faithfuls. Drank enough @goodboyvodka to power John’s custom golf carts and sank some birdies along the way. Love my team!! @txsamlee @donniereismusic @chazbragg @visualsbytyre @greatdanemane @pgatour ⛳️🏌️‍♂️.

🎥 - @visualsbytyre.
Europe is magical.
Friends always and forever. Love you so much @kleversworld 🌹. Back to business!!

It’s my birthday!! Grateful for my friends and music and cooking and golf and all the other stuff that keeps me going.  Thank you to all the people who helped me grow throughout the years. Love yall, lots more to come!! ❤️🌹.
I swear they love me @zackdeaton @j.ebbert.tattoos ❤️.
Oh we talkin teams?! #warstory.
Grant me serenity. #lightsoff.

Now that I can finally post this, when I was out in England, my brother @the_business_of_livin took me on a surprise tour of @duchesschina1888 in Stoke on Trent. Everything there is bone china, made completely by hand. We got to see the whole process, and he even had two of these plates screened with my album cover on it. At the very end of the tour, we walked into an art studio and was greeted by my new friend Lee Price. Lee was in the process of painting all of the new plates for the King of England and Buckingham Palace completely from scratch.  Yes you red that correctly, and to be clear each plate cost the royal family £4000 and takes a month to make. He invited me to sit down and personalize my plates, one for @yelawolf as a gift for doing a feature for me, and one for my own personal plate. We made our paint from scratch from powdered paint and I went to town. Definitely an experience I will never forget.

I was fortunate enough to do an inerview with @chaos.n.havoc and The Wrapper. We talked about coming up as an artist, traveling and touring, New York City, and Waffle House. Please take a minute and have a look, I’m grateful for the time taken for the interview. Link in Linktree in bio and story 💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻.
Off the record, I got the hardest new single on the way to start 2024 with a fucking eruption. Produced by @taystybeats. #lightsoff.

I think not being afraid to try new things and scaring yourself a little is such a great part of the creative process. I’m really feeling the newer sounds I’m bringing and looking forward to getting closer to beginning of the release process. Me and @brassxbeard had such a great session the other day I left almost feeling almost manic. @taystybeats has so much to offer on all of these records and I’m brining my A-game to all of them. It’s absolutely undeniable. All photos taken in studio by @filmdirt 📸📸📸📸📸.
